%H A393835 <a href="/index/Per#IntegerPermutation">Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers</a>
%F A393835 a(n) < 3^k iff n < 3^k for any k >= 0.
%e A393835 The first terms, scattered on the variant of Sierpinski carpet A393834 are:
